{"type": "article", "id": 18728, "title": "可拆装的家具系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-09T07:10:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122401VA9LazdU6wFnrObD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是新加坡的设计师 JiaHao LIAO 推出的家具系列，有很强的拆装性。可以将椅子的靠背拆下来放到下面，变成一个茶几，方方正正的感觉有点像明式家具。餐桌的腿也是可拆下来的，侧着放就成立一张矮茶几或者咖啡桌。还有沙发中间的桌子，也可以与沙发互换顺序，总之是符合现代人需要的一种灵活的家具。<a href=\"http://www.jiahaoliao.com/work_1+1+1.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122358BD7ujhdxENwJXyvn.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122358VFCvSNOYj2K1d4gq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122359i5QvCpeDmf4tw6lH.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122359FJtjNbvVIxYrkd8E.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.855\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122400HbcsdMnkF9hCZqW5.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.855\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}